---
title: Teach computing. With confidence.
layout: layout
fixed: true
---

<section class='header-block'>
  <h1 class="animated fadeIn">
    Teach computing. With confidence.
  </h1>
  <h2 class="animated fadeIn">
    The cloud coding & content platform for teaching computer science
  </h2>
  <div class="action-buttons animated fadeInUp">
    <%= link_to 'Schools', '/school', class: 'button button-large' %>
    <%= link_to 'Universities', '/university', class: 'button button-large' %>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="index-content">
  <div id="index-content-start"></div>


  <div
    class="index-section index-section-content wow fadeIn"
    data-wow-duration="2s"
    data-wow-delay=".5s"
    >
    <h2>Unique learning experience</h2>

    <%= image_tag 'assets/index/laptop-ide.png', class: "index-section-content-img" %>
    <div class="index-section-content-copy">
      <p>
        Codio course content is made interactive with live code and preview windows
        &mdash; allowing students to test and trial what they're learning; built in
        challenges also stimulate engagement and create opportunities for "learning by doing".
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <div class="index-section index-section-curriculum">
    <div
      class="index-section-left wow fadeIn"
      data-wow-duration="1s"
      data-wow-delay="0s"
      >
      <h2>Full curriculum coverage</h2>
      <p>
        From Computer systems, computational and algorithmic thinking challenges,
courses on Python and Javascript, as well as all the project workspace you
        need &mdash; Codio empowers you to teach the full Computing curriculum with
        confidence.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="index-section-right index-section-curriculum-img wow fadeInRight"
      data-wow-duration="1s"
      data-wow-delay=".8s"
      ></div>
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <div
    class="index-section index-section-assessments wow fadeIn"
    data-wow-duration="2s"
    data-wow-delay=".5s"
    >
    <div class="index-section-left">
      <h2>Integrated assessments</h2>
      <p>
        Teacher dashboards display clear and simple information about Class and
        Student progress &mdash; presenting scores for built-in auto-marked
        assessments that enable you to focus more time on teaching and supporting
        and less on administration.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="index-section-right index-section-assessments-img"></div>
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <div class="index-section index-section-projects">
    <div
      class="index-section-projects-top wow fadeIn"
      data-wow-duration="2s"
      data-wow-delay=".5s"
      >
      <h2>Perfect for projects</h2>
      <p>
        Accessible anywhere, with pre-configured environments containing all
        the software and other components a student will need, each user enjoys
        a dedicated virtual server for their project work &mdash; ideal in the
        classroom or at home.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="index-section-projects-bottom">
      <div
        class="index-section-projects-img wow fadeInUp"
        data-wow-duration="1s"
        data-wow-delay=".5s"
        >
        <%= image_tag 'assets/index/live-code.png' %>
        <figcaption>Live code</figcaption>
      </div>
      <div
        class="index-section-projects-img wow fadeInUp"
        data-wow-duration="1s"
        data-wow-delay="1s"
        >
        <%= image_tag 'assets/index/preview-windows.png' %>
        <figcaption>Preview windows</figcaption>
      </div>
      <div
        class="index-section-projects-img wow fadeInUp"
        data-wow-duration="1s"
        data-wow-delay="1.5s"
        >
        <%= image_tag 'assets/index/challenges.png' %>
        <figcaption>Challenges</figcaption>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <div class="index-section index-section-partners">
    <h2>
      We are proud members and partners of
    </h2>
    <div class="index-section-partners-img">
      <%= image_tag 'assets/index/partners-ocr.png' %>
      <%= image_tag 'assets/index/partners-cas.png' %>
      <%= image_tag 'assets/index/partners-naace.png' %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <%= partial "call-to-action" %>
</section>
